:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:312:"Now that the latest release of Connections is out the door, and doing quite well I may add, I can shift my focus to working on the next update to Form. What can you expect? The frequently requested email notifications. With the next version you&#8217;ll have the option to set up two email notifications. The ...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Steven Zahm";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2104:"<p>Now that the latest release of Connections is out the door, and doing quite well I may add, I can shift my focus to working on the next update to Form. What can you expect? The frequently requested email notifications. With the next version you&#8217;ll have the option to set up two email notifications. The first is an auto responder which is sent back to the user submitting the new entry thanking them for their submission. The second is an email to the site admin, which is configurable, letting them know they have a new entry in the moderation queue. Well, that is about it. The screen shots can tell the rest of the story&#8230;</p><p><a href="http://cdn1.connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Capture-Form-Email-Auto-Responder.png"><img width="220" height="150" alt="Screen Capture - Form Email Auto Responder" src="http://connections-pro.com/wp-content/themes/striking/includes/timthumb.php?src=/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Capture-Form-Email-Auto-Responder.png&amp;h=150&amp;w=220&amp;zc=1" /></a><a href="http://cdn2.connections-pro.com/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Capture-Form-New-Submission-Email.png"><img width="220" height="150" alt="Screen Capture - Form New Submission Email" src="http://connections-pro.com/